{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bc94a02fee","title":"关于拍摄三反纪录片问题复高岗电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"085042d929","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":27,"articleId":"bc94a02fee"}],"tags":[{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"7a9a962257","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指高岗1952年2月26日关于凯丰向毛泽东反映对三反纪录片摄制提纲（草案）的意见的经过情况给毛泽东的电报。电报转述了凯丰对纪录片拟出现某些领导人的镜头有意见，要求向毛泽东反映，并说他有意见向主席提出，这是应该的。"},{"id":"239c214141","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"凯丰，即何克全，当时任中共中央东北局委员、沈阳市委书记。"},{"id":"e29f69ed0d","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央宣传部1952年2月19日关于三反运动大型纪录片摄制提纲（草案）。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ea41f378e4","type":"title","text":"关于拍摄三反纪录片问题复高岗电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee"},{"id":"7a9a962257","type":"paragraph","text":"高岗同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee"},{"id":"239c214141","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿六日的电报收到。你的意见很好。凯丰电报中主张拍军队一点是正确的，已采纳，恩来同志已将提纲作了修改（加上拍军队和拍民主人士），我已看过发出。凯丰电报中的其他部分则是不正确的，已托陈云陈伯达二同志向你及凯丰说明。凯丰有意见（不论意见正确与否）打电报给我是好的，他以后有意见还可打电报来。有意见不打电报则不好。以上请转告凯丰。三月中句或下句中央可能召开一次会议，那时你再来京，目前不要来。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee"},{"id":"e29f69ed0d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee"},{"id":"d7364ce60b","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee"}],"page":{"id":"5260bf5910","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"bc94a02fee","start":446,"end":446}}}},"__N_SSG":true}